&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;安装dnscat2
&amp;gt;apt-get -y install ruby-dev git make g++
&amp;gt;gem install bundler
&amp;gt;git clone https://github.com/iagox86/dnscat2.git
&amp;gt;cd dnscat2/server
