&lt;h3 id=&#34;password-filter-dll&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#password-filter-dll&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Password Filter DLL&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;https://github.com/3gstudent/PasswordFilter
visualstudio生成解决方案
DLL放在%windir%\system32\下
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Lsa下的Notification Packages，添加Win32Project3
