&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL2ZveC1pdC9hY2xwd24ucHk=&#34;&gt;aclpwn.py&lt;/span&gt; - Active Directory ACL exploitation with BloodHound&lt;/li&gt;
